description: Strahler stream order of the site from the provider dataset (unit: none).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType StreamOrder.

description: Average bankfull width depth ratio for the reach (unit: meters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType AvgBFWDRatio.

description: Average bankfull height measured from water surface across transects (unit: meters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType BFHeight.

description: Average bankfull width across transects for the reach (unit: meters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType BFWidth.

description: Number of cross sections included in the average bankfull width calculation (units: count of measurements)
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType countTransectsBFWidth.

description: Mean slope of water surface from the bottom of the reach to the top of the reach (expressed as percent, unit: none).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType Grad.

description: Mean thalweg depth. Metric of how deep the water was at the site (unit: meters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType MeanThalwegDepth.

description: Length of sampling reach measured along the thalweg (unit: meters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType ReachLen.

description: Average wetted width across transects (unit: meters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType WetWidth.

description: Percent of the sample reach (linear extent) classified as pool habitat (expressed as a percent, unit: none, min: 0, max: 100).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType PctPool.

description: Average of the residual pool depth values for all pools in a reach. Residual pool depth the difference of the pool tail depth from the max depth (unit: meters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType RPD.

description: Measured angle of the stream bank (unit: degrees).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType BankAngle.

description: Percent of 42 banks lacking visible signs of active erosion (e.g., slump, slough, fracture) expressed as a percent (unit: none, min: 0, max: 100).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType PctStab.

description: Bed surface particle size corresponding to the 16th percentile of measured particles (unit: millimeters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType D16.

description: Median diameter of bed surface particle size corresponding to the areal median (50th percentile of measured particles) (unit: millimeters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType D50.

description: Bed surface particle size corresponding to the 84th percentile of measured particles (unit: millimeters).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType D84.

description: Percent of the stream bed area that is composed of particles with a b axis greater than 4098 millimeters (expressed as percent, units: none, min: 0, max: 100).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType PctBdrk.

description: Percent of the stream bed area that is comprised of particles with a b axis less than 2 millimeters (expressed as percent, units: none, min: 0, max: 100).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType PctFines2.

description: Average percent fine sediment (less than 6 millimeters) on the pool tail (expressed as a percent, unit: none, min: 0, max: 100).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType PctFines6.

description: Average percent fine sediment (less than 2 millimeters) on the pool tail (expressed as percent, unit: none).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType PoolTailFines2.

description: Average percent fine sediment (less than 6 millimeters) on the pool tail (expressed as a percent, unit: none).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType PoolTailFines6.

description: Measure of the concentration of ionized materials in water, or the ability of water to conduct electrical current. Used as a measure of mineral / ionic concentration (unit: ppm or parts per million).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType Conductivity.

description: Measured pH value (unit: none, min: 0, max:14).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType pH.

description: Measured specific conductance value. The specific conductance is conductivity standardized to 25 degrees C (unit: uS/cm or microSiemens per centimeter).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType SpecificConductance.

description: Measured total nitrogen value (unit: ug/L or micrograms per liter).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType TotalNitrogen.

description: Measured total phosphorous value (unit: ug/L or micrograms per liter).
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType TotalPhosphorous.

description: Average water clarity as measured by the suspended solids in the water column (unit: NTU or Nephelometric Turbidity unit)
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to the measurementType Turbidity.

measurementType: A unique numeric identifier assigned to measurementType Sin
description: NA
enumerateddefinition: A unique numeric identifier assigned to measurementType Sin.
